      "message": "Is this name groups.json a good name for an override for the PapDb.json? \nMy rationale for the name pick was to keep it different to avoid any confusion if needed to debug runtime.   I also thought that the name was more meaningful, since it is really provisioning groups.   I think the syntax is the same as the REST API to create/update a group.   In any case, let me know if you have different preferences.",
